node.title: Man charged with murder after baby dies in Auckland
node.description: A 21-year-old man has been arrested and charged with murder after the death of a 10-month-old in Auckland.
node.content:
["A 21-year-old man has been arrested and charged with murder after the death of a 10-month-old in Auckland.", "", "
(File image) Photo: 123rf.com
", "Chance Kamanaka O Ke Akura Aipolani-Nielson died at Starship Hospital last week, after being admitted there with injuries.", "The 21-year-old is expected to appear in the North Shore District Court tomorrow."]
